		<th class="thHead" align="left">Uhhhh, wow...ummm...yeah...</th>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td class="row1"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">The Rise of the Upstart Gods: Convergence
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
The shards of Aerynth are entering a period of spiritual upheaval! For the first time since the Turning, the scattered peoples of Aerynth have felt the presence of their Gods. The mysterious Votaries, emissaries of the Order of Varnai, have built shrines to many of Aerynth's gods and legendary figures. 
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
The Varnites claim absolute neutrality in the struggles that rage across Aerynth, and claim to serve as intermediaries between mortals and the Divine, offering the boons of the lost Gods to their followers. Shrines have appeared to many of the old gods, long forgotten, including Saedron and Thurin, while other, younger demigods have appeared, including Jackal, Saint Malorn, and even Morloch himself. Conservative sages refer to the new crop of idols as the "Upstart Gods." At first there were many who doubted the motives of the Varnites, or the power of their shrines. Those doubts were swept away as the faithful earned powerful boons for their worship and service.
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
And now the Votaries whisper new, even stranger tales: the shrines are working, and the steady stream of offerings is actually weakening the barriers that prevent the Upstart Gods from setting foot on Aerynth! A massive wave of divine favor, called the Convergence, shall soon sweep over all the fragments of Aerynth, blessing and nourishing the soul of every living mortal. Lost fragments of the lost Weltwyrdangssaga are being found in undreamed of numbers, allowing mortals to take on godlike powers by linking to the All-Father's ancient runes. Some prophets and heretics whisper that other, stranger forces are at work, and that the upcoming Convergence shall be a time of wonders indeed…  
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
Starting this Friday, the experience across all worlds will be doubled!  This phase will last approximately a week and a half and end on May 5th.  In addition to this, around the 28th of this month, the Upstarts will increase the amount of Godly and lesser Runestones that appear throughout the worlds.
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
Finally, on the 28th of April, there will Treasure Hunts across all servers.  In various adventuring areas, special armor and weapons will be hidden upon different creatures.  A list of these items will be given out closer to the Treasure Hunt.
<br />

<br />
 
<br />

<br />
Let the Time of the Upstarts commence!
<br />
By: Vosx</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
