<br />

<br />
The war has begun. KGB set up bulwarks and began attempting to inflict asset damage on Skyfang HQ. They did this unsuccessfully.
<br />

<br />
I encourage all of you to log into vengeance this weekend and move all the scattered characters back together and get ready to own KGB and PoR.
<br />

<br />
If you log in and are looking to get tagged look for NoMas or OwnedNewbie (my lock), NoMercy, Velvet, Nerd, BoomBoom, Blut, Mindstrike, or look for skyfang summoners and tell em you are TSB.
